<p><?php echo $appname; ?> does not download actual music, it only downloads .torrent/.nzb files. In order to automate your downloads you need to also configure <?php echo $appname; ?> to communicate with a download program, like SABnzbd, NZBGet or Transmission. Please check <a href="https://github.com/rembo10/headphones/wiki/Usage-guide" target="_new"><?php echo $appname; ?>&apos; usage guide</a> for more information.</p>
<p>It is strongly recommended to password-protect <?php echo $appname; ?> if it is going to be exposed to the internet. This can be done in the &quot;General&quot; settings page.</p>